{"tid":2435342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[肝膽排石法] 愛莉莎莎粉絲向台大醫院檢舉台大住院醫師蒼藍鴿，全案已進入調查。","createTime":"2021-03-06T07:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T22:59:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1c6ee990a9383f90aea6a9b320e69c7432d053","tid":2435342,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"擁有 117 萬訂閱者的知名Youtuber「愛莉莎莎」日前公布喝橄欖油排膽結石影片，引發台大醫院兒科醫師「蒼藍鴿」反擊，指責她傳遞錯誤醫療知識，最後愛莉莎莎下架影片並道歉，而蒼藍鴿隨後也發布影片向愛莉莎莎致歉，自承未先告知對方，導致她被多人攻擊，但就在風波看似告一段落，《蘋果新聞網》卻接獲自稱是<strong><span class=\"red\">愛莉莎莎粉絲</span></strong>的爆料，<span class=\"red\"><strong>指控蒼藍鴿是公務人員，經營Youtube賺外快是違法的，對此台大院方已展開調查</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20210301/6XIVMUIFYJERXILFQ2Y5ZFJUW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20210301%2F6XIVMUIFYJERXILFQ2Y5ZFJUW4%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=b983c2dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20210301%2F6XIVMUIFYJERXILFQ2Y5ZFJUW4%2F&h=635319f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20210301/6XIVMUIFYJERXILFQ2Y5ZFJUW4/</a>"},{"pid":"47eba360740955f3f55c77bad5a14e47e81957cb","tid":2435342,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"有讀者向《蘋果》投訴指，蒼藍鴿頂著台大住院醫師名義，於Youtube經營商業頻道，可能違反《公務員服務法》，依此法公務員不得經營商業或投機事業，違者應予撤職。<br />\n<br />\n該讀者也說，「這算是愛莉莎莎粉絲的反擊」，若《蘋果》要問細節，可找台大醫院，畢竟這是台大該處理的事。<br />\n<br />\n台大醫院回應，已接獲民眾反映小兒部醫師吳其穎（蒼藍鴿本名）相關事宜，已盡速處理，並依照民眾提供內容了解中，也感謝民眾來信建議。"},{"pid":"08379750f1fd722e6386c671d14315b1925dafc9","tid":2435342,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"衛福部醫事司劉越萍說，公立醫院為留住醫師人才，可能會給予住院醫師公務員身分，但這因人而異，並非一體適用，蒼藍鴿有無公務員身分，要看台大醫院有無安排，至於醫師經營臉書、拍片是否違規，則交由院方審視。"},{"pid":"5b2b6f6365b19b893f08329dfbf8e8fa9f77ef24","tid":2435342,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"對於遭檢舉公務員違法賺外快，蒼藍鴿今日在臉書粉絲團以高EQ回應，「聽說我被檢舉惹？不過那不重要，沒人能阻止我繼續科普」，照常發布圖文和影音解釋何謂有機磷中毒。"},{"pid":"c9300018043636680ecf989b72c8a83203401e2c","tid":2435342,"uid":62532,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d fans都白撚痴<br />\n人地救左你一命仲去告人"},{"pid":"3d6cab0d51c1dd217967a6585bae03550bda7560","tid":2435342,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"台大醫院今天表示，確實有收到民眾檢舉吳其穎涉嫌利用YouTube營利，目前已展開調查，但院方強調，台大醫師有些是公務員有些不是，因公務員名額有限，住院醫院都不是公務員，即使升上主治醫師，有些也沒有公務員身分，吳其穎目前還是住院醫師，因此沒有公務員不得兼職或從事商業行為的問題，目前初步認定未違法。<br />\n<br />\n但不具名台大醫師表示，不論是否具公務員身分，台大醫師都是廣義的公務員，根據行政院人事行政局96年4月13日所做的第0960008394號書函，即使是約聘僱人員也適用《公務員服務法》，業外不得有商業或營利行為，前台大感染科醫師林氏璧就是因為經營旅遊社群網站接受業配、分潤，遭到懲戒，後來離開台大，蒼藍鴿（吳其穎）其實也是類似情形。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210301001186-260405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210301001186-260405&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=1c8bc764\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210301001186-260405</a>"},{"pid":"8c11e4eee809ed3039686ac4662100e787bdbc8a","tid":2435342,"uid":114097,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c9300018043636680ecf989b72c8a83203401e2c","tid":2435342,"uid":62532,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d fans都白撚痴<br />\n人地救左你一命仲去告人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"啲Fans真係驚愛莉莎莎死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要加多腳"},{"pid":"ba306ec0ac94fa3f29d67f6d708c40c00d10bc43","tid":2435342,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"因為呢件事, 己訂閱蒼藍鴿"},{"pid":"2f19d6da9989ec16d526252d49ff52280e51a04d","tid":2435342,"uid":393395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"好撚柒 護主護到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2bd82a67f11d34c1f28715e0a413ef7e6f3b33","tid":2435342,"uid":209657,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"愛莉莎莎可以準備搵工先，做pr適合佢"},{"pid":"41f681ceae6b352d4e7c767f48ff20d7bbe43497","tid":2435342,"uid":187554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"有律師幫佢做野 告佢唔入"},{"pid":"05ca1ac57a40bac94b502bb69140ca99d39b0907","tid":2435342,"uid":85586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8c11e4eee809ed3039686ac4662100e787bdbc8a","tid":2435342,"uid":114097,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c9300018043636680ecf989b72c8a83203401e2c","tid":2435342,"uid":62532,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d fans都白撚痴<br />\n人地救左你一命仲去告人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"啲Fans真係驚愛莉莎莎死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要加多腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"喺𠵱家fans行為=明星行為嘅風氣下<br />\n就算唔係佢做都死得好慘<br />\n除非佢出聲明同班所謂fans割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f866c7460cc090970b94d58c7470a7736dd6213e","tid":2435342,"uid":195493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"笑死，仲話fan，嫌佢死得唔夠快插多刀<img 